OL,10,FA couple from Staffordshire have
OL,11,Fdescribed the "horror show" they
OL,12,Fwitnessed as an ambulance exploded
OL,13,Foutside their house.
OL,15,FDavid and Marilyn Brinklow's 91-year-
OL,16,Fold neighbour was being dropped off by
OL,17,Fthe ambulance on Thursday 14 March
OL,18,Fwhen a pedestrian alerted the driver
OL,19,Fthat the vehicle was smoking.
