OL,6,FThe couple, from Barton-under-
OL,7,FNeedwood, closed their curtains as the
OL,8,Fengine caught fire, then exploded.
OL,10,FFootage shared exclusively with ITV
OL,11,FNews Central by David and Marilyn show
OL,12,Fanother explosion follow.
OL,14,FThe roof of the ambulance then blew
OL,15,Foff and landed on their garage -
OL,16,Fleaving a huge hole in the roof.
OL,18,FTheir hedges, trees and lawn all
OL,19,Fcaught fire, and the back of their car
OL,20,Falso melted.
