OL,6,FDavid and Marilyn's windows were
OL,7,Fdamaged in the fire, and they remain
OL,8,Fboarded up as the couple wait until
OL,9,Fthe 11 April to get them replaced.
OL,11,FThe house is completely smoke damaged,
OL,12,Fwhilst electricity to the garage is
OL,13,Fstill cut off and they are forced to
OL,14,Frun an adapter to keep the freezer
OL,15,Fgoing.
OL,17,FMarilyn said: "It was like a Hitchcock
OL,18,Ffilm. I suffer with my nerves and it
OL,19,Fdidn't do me any good.
