OL,6,F"I keep having flashbacks. There was
OL,7,Fnothing left of the ambulance and all
OL,8,Fthe bits of it like a volcano were
OL,9,Fflying off like glass and started
OL,10,Fburning our nets. Its horrible to talk
OL,11,Fabout."
OL,13,FDavid added: "It went off like a roman
OL,14,Fcandle. I was shocked - it was like a
OL,15,Fhorror show."
OL,17,FWatch the moment the ambulance goes up
OL,18,Fin flames as firefighters work to
