OL,10,Fengine of our ambulance caught fire.
OL,12,F"Unfortunately, some of the
OL,13,Fneighbouring properties suffered
OL,14,Fdamage, which we are now managing
OL,15,Fthrough our insurer.
OL,17,F"All our ambulances undergo robust
OL,18,Fsafety checks on a regular basis and
OL,19,Four absolute priority is the safety of
